cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper deals with machine translation, specifically for low-resource languages, and uses neural network models. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves deep learning techniques, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of character-level models, which could be relevant to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) sub-categories.
